    "description": "We at Oberoi Mall Asia Pacific Associates are looking for an experienced Real Estate Agent based out of Ghaziabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Oberoi Mall Asia Pacific Associates:\nOberoi Mall Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oberoi Mall Asia Pacific Associates!",
